				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7948440/error:field-cannot-be-lloyd#post-4028290</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 18 Oct 2018 22:43:41 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Mark Penrice</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1858819</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Clever way to twist the &quot;one survivor&quot; thing &#8230; I mean, everyone else also stays alive&#8230; but if they all end up melting together, who's to say where Lloyd ends and any other human begins? They ultimately end up as a single, massive hivemind&#8230;</p> <p>But who is Sam?</p> <p>edit: also that mouseover is both clever and subtle, how did you get it to animate both ways?!</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
